diff_analysis.evidence: The new code adds strict whitelisting of allowed cache filenames before constructing the path, which mitigates path traversal (CWE-22) rather than introducing it. No dynamic code execution, regex processing, web output, or request-handling logic is added, so none of CWE-79, CWE-94, CWE-1333, CWE-22, or CWE-352 are introduced by this patch.
